    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted given the standardized single-condition nature of ASTM F1717 and the strong quantitative agreement across all QoIs (all E/uval < 1.96, all percent differences < 10%). The overall credibility evidence, supported by systematic literature benchmarking across published F1717 datasets, is judged sufficient to support regulatory submission at Medium assurance level.",
